citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 350pm on
5/20/2024. The inspector attempted to contact the licensee/registrant by Phone, text, and email. Failure to provide access
to the facility, animals, and records for inspection is a serious violation of the AWA and regulations. Failure to comply may
result in enforcement action.
End Section
